# Code-Gen-AI Cursor Rules

## Mandatory lifecycle

Do not write code until there is a plan:

1. Define
2. Plan
3. Build
4. Verify
5. Review
6. Ship

## Architecture rules

- React/Vite frontend.
- Tailwind styling.
- Radix/Shadcn-style local components.
- TFRS Tactical Command Deck aesthetic.
- Server-side provider gateway.
- Zod schemas.
- Sandpack MVP preview.
- WebContainers only when full browser Node runtime is explicitly needed.

## Forbidden shortcuts

- No one-shot prompt-to-code.
- No direct commit to main.
- No unreviewed heavy UI library.
- No exposed provider keys.
- No production backend calls from preview code.
